example.eg: There were no applications, other than the internal ones received earlier.  Other than a couple seated at a table by the window, the restaurant was deserted.
example.egtrans: 除了之前收到的内部申请外，没有其他申请了。除了坐在靠窗位置的那对夫妻外，整家餐馆空空如也。

example.eg: We have with us today a man we all know, none other than the champion racer of the entire league.
